{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775809158294,"sessionID":"ses_289893b44ffeFEX28qQi8Ul3j8","part":{"id":"prt_d7676cfc4001NZf07bC82NZ2Md","messageID":"msg_d7676c5ae001FA35JV6v7L03wn","sessionID":"ses_289893b44ffeFEX28qQi8Ul3j8","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_fc5d3cf98add45bda0f1fb1f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube AR-001","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project in the current working directory. I need to understand what was completed for AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime type definition in pkg/apis.\n\nSearch thoroughly for:\n1. Any AgentRuntime CRD type definitions (Go structs, types, API definitions)\n2. Files under pkg/apis/ related to AgentRuntime\n3. Any related test files\n4. Any documentation or comments about what was done vs deferred\n\nLook for patterns like:\n- `AgentRuntime` struct definitions\n- `type AgentRuntime` declarations\n- CRD-related files (types.go, zz_generated, register.go, etc.)\n- Any TODO comments or deferred items\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of:\n- What files exist and what they contain\n- What appears to be completed\n- Any TODOs, deferred items, or incomplete work\n- The overall state of the AR-001 implementation","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2898919f8ffeRaEvvSisq7WT6Y (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a complete picture. Here is my comprehensive summary:\n\n---\n\n## AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition -- Comprehensive Analysis\n\n### 1. Files That Exist and Their Contents\n\n#### Source Files (under `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n\n| File | Lines | Purpose |\n|------|-------|---------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | 3 | Package-level codegen markers: `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package`, `+groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/api