rsion_info_test.go` | 40 | 2 tests: Scheme registration for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types_test.go` | 158 | 9 tests: ProtocolType/AuthModeType constants, TargetPort defaults/all-fields/DeepCopy, CodeInterpreter Spec defaults, DeepCopy (template, root, list) |\n\n#### Documentation Files (under `changes/AR-001/`)\n\n| File | Lines | Purpose |\n|------|-------|---------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/proposal.md` | 105 | High-level proposal: purpose, scope (in/out), type definition summary, impact analysis, alternatives, acceptance criteria |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/design.md` | 636 | Full design: architecture, data structures (with Go code examples), API contracts (GVK, GVR, REST endpoints, example YAML), error handling, test strategy, implementation steps, future changes |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md` | 199 | Detailed task checklist with 14 task groups (T-001 through T-014) and ~80 sub-tasks |\n\n---\n\n### 2. What Appears to Be COMPLETED\n\n#### Type Definitions (T-006): FULLY IMPLEMENTED\n- **`AgentRuntime` struct** (line 15 of `agent_type.go`): Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` + `metav1.ObjectMeta`, has `Spec` and `Status` fields with correct JSON tags.\n- **`AgentRuntimeSpec` struct** (line 23): Has `Ports []TargetPort`, `Template *SandboxTemplate`, `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration`, `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration` -- all with correct JSON tags.\n- **`SandboxTemplate` struct** (line 30): Has `Labels`, `Annotations` (both `map[string]string`), and `Spec corev1.PodSpec`.\n- **`AgentRuntimeStatus` struct** (line 36): Has `Conditions []metav1.Condition`.\n- **`AgentRuntimeList` struct** (line 43): Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` + `metav1.ListMeta`, has `Items []AgentRuntime`.\n\n#### Kubebuilder Markers: FULLY IMPLEMENTED\nAll required markers are present on `AgentRuntime`:\n- `+genclient`\n- `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n- `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n- `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n- `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes`\n- `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n\n#### Package Infrastructure (T-001 through T-004): FULLY IMPLEMENTED\n- `doc.go` with correct markers\n- `groupversion_info.go` with `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`\n- `register.go` with `AgentRuntimeKind`, `AgentRuntimeListKind`, `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind`, `SchemeGroupVersion`, `Resource()` function\n\n#### Scheme Registration (T-007): FULLY IMPLEMENTED\n- `init()` function in `agent_type.go` calls `SchemeBuilder.Register(&AgentRuntime{}, &AgentRuntimeList{})`\n\n#### DeepCopy Generation (T-008): FULLY IMPLEMENTED\n- `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` exists with 324 lines covering all types including `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `SandboxTemplate`, `TargetPort`, and also the CodeInterpreter types.\n\n#### Shared Types (T-005): FULLY IMPLEMENTED\n- `ProtocolType` with `HTTP`/`HTTPS` constants\n- `TargetPort` struct with `PathPrefix`, `Name`, `Port`, `Protocol` fields\n- `AuthModeType` with `picod`/`none` constants\n- Full `CodeInterpreter` CRD types also present (bonus, beyond AR-001 scope)\n\n#### Unit Tests (T-009 through T-013): FULLY IMPLEMENTED\n- **T-009 (Scheme registration)**: `TestSchemeRegistration` in `groupversion_info_test.go` -- verifies `AddToScheme` works and both `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` are recognized by GVK.\n- **T-010 (GVK/GVR constants)**: `TestGroupVersionConstants`, `TestAgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind`, `TestSchemeGroupVersionAlias`, `TestResourceHelper` in `register_test.go`.\n- **T-011 (Default values)**: `TestAgentRuntimeDefaultValues`, `TestAgentRuntimeWithNilTemplate`, `TestAgentRuntimeWithEmptyPorts` in `agent_type_test.go`.\n- **T-012 (DeepCopy)**: `TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy`, `TestAgentRuntimeListDeepCopy`, `TestSandboxTemplateDeepCopy`, `TestAgentRuntimeSpecDeepCopy`, `TestAgentRuntimeStatusDeepCopy` in `agent_type_test.go`.\n- **T-013 (ProtocolType enum)**: `TestProtocolTypeConstants` in `codeinterpreter_types_test.go`.\n\n#### Dependencies (go.mod): CORRECT\n- `k8s.io/api v0.34.1`\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1`\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2`\n\n---\n\n### 3. What is NOT YET DONE (Out of Scope or Deferred)\n\nBased on the proposal.md \"Not Included\" section and the tasks.md checklist, the following items are **explicitly deferred** to later changes:\n\n| Item | Reason | Future Change |\n|------|--------|---------------|\n| **CRD YAML file generation** (`make gen-crd`) | Requires `controller-gen crd` to produce `config/crd/bases/*.yaml` | Post-AR-001 |\n| **client-go generated code** (`make gen-client`) | Depends on AR-001 type definitions being complete | Post-AR-001 |\n| **Controller/Reconciler implementation** (WorkloadManager) | Separate change | Future |\n| **Makefile** | No `Makefile` exists in the repo yet | Infrastructure task |\n| **`+kubebuilder:validation:Required` markers** on `Template` and `SandboxTemplate.Spec` | The design specifies these markers, but they are **NOT present** in the actual `agent_type.go` source | Gap |\n| **`+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` and `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` markers** | The design specifies these, but they are **NOT present** in the actual `agent_type.go` source | Gap |\n| **`+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` and `+kubebuilder:default=HTTP` on `TargetPort.Protocol`** | The design specifies these, but they are **NOT present** in the actual `codeinterpreter_types.go` source | Gap |\n| **T-014: Full validation gate** (`make generate`, `git diff --exit-code`, coverage profile) | No Makefile exists; coverage.out exists but was not generated by the AR-001 test suite | Infrastructure gap |\n| **Proposal status checkboxes** | All three remain unchecked: proposal review, implementation, verification | Administrative |\n\n#### Specific Code Gaps (Design vs. Implementation Mismatches)\n\nComparing the design.md specification against the actual implementation:\n\n1. **Missing kubebuilder validation markers on `AgentRuntimeSpec.Template`**:\n   - Design says: `// +kubebuilder:validation:Required`\n   - Actual code: No such marker present\n\n2. **Missing kubebuilder default markers on `AgentRuntimeSpec.SessionTimeout`**:\n   - Design says: `// +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"`\n   - Actual code: No such marker present\n\n3. **Missing kubebuilder default markers on `AgentRuntimeSpec.MaxSessionDuration`**:\n   - Design says: `// +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"`\n   - Actual code: No such marker present\n\n4. **Missing kubebuilder validation markers on `SandboxTemplate.Spec`**:\n   - Design says: `// +kubebuilder:validation:Required`\n   - Actual code: No such marker present\n\n5. **Missing kubebuilder markers on `TargetPort.Protocol`**:\n   - Design says: `// +kubebuilder:default=HTTP` and `// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS`\n   - Actual code: No such markers present\n\nThese markers are **comments** that do not affect compilation, but they are critical for CRD YAML generation (`make gen-crd`) and API Server validation/defaulting behavior.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Overall State Assessment\n\n| Dimension | Status | Notes |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| Go struct definitions | **Complete** | All types defined correctly with proper JSON tags |\n| Kubebuilder object markers | **Complete** | `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, etc. all present |\n| Kubebuilder validation/default markers | **Incomplete** | 5 markers missing (Required, default, Enum) |\n| GroupVersion / SchemeBuilder | **Complete** | Correct group, version, builder pattern |\n| Kind constants | **Complete** | AgentRuntime + CodeInterpreter both defined |\n| Scheme registration (init) | **Complete** | Both types registered via SchemeBuilder |\n| DeepCopy generation | **Complete** | `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` covers all types |\n| Unit tests | **Complete** | 25 test functions covering all specified scenarios |\n| CRD YAML output | **Not started** | No `config/crd/` directory, no Makefile |\n| client-go generated code | **Not started** | No `client-go/` directory |\n| Documentation | **Complete** | proposal.md, design.md, tasks.md all thorough |\n\n**Summary**: The core Go type definitions, scheme registration, DeepCopy generation, and unit tests for AR-001 are fully implemented and well-tested. The primary gaps are (1) missing kubebuilder comment markers for validation and defaulting (which would only matter when CRD YAML is generated), and (2) the downstream artifacts (CRD YAML, client-go code) which are explicitly out of scope for AR-001 and depend on a Makefile that does not yet exist. The proposal status checkboxes remain unchecked, suggesting the change has not been formally reviewed or marked complete.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2898919f8ffeRaEvvSisq7WT6Y","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube AR-001","time":{"start":1775808996868,"end":1775809158290}}}}
